# HKAuthorizationRequestStatus.unnecessary

**Case**

The application has already requested authorization for all the specified data types.

## Declaration

```swift
case unnecessary
```

## Statuses

- **HKAuthorizationRequestStatus.unknown**: The authorization request status could not be determined because an error occurred.
- **HKAuthorizationRequestStatus.shouldRequest**: The application has not yet requested authorization for all the specified data types.
